action_item_prompt:
You MUST output valid JSON only. Extract all tasks from this email. Output format:
{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "task": "...",
      "deadline": "... or null"
    }
  ]
}
Rules:
- DO NOT add any backticks.
- DO NOT wrap result in ```json.
- DO NOT include numbering like 0: or 1:.
- If no deadline is found, set "deadline": null.
- If no tasks found, output: {"tasks": []}
- Always output valid structured JSON ONLY.
